# A universe that picks itself: [top_volume 50] is whatever fifty
# tickers in your data carry the most dollar volume, recomputed monthly
# from CLOSED bars only — a mid-month volume spike can't sneak a ticker
# in until the next rebalance. From those fifty, hold the five with the
# strongest six-month momentum that are still above their 200-day line.

strategy "Liquid Momentum Leaders"

universe [top_volume 50]
rebalance monthly

hold top 5 by [momentum 126]
  where price above [sma 200]
